  "remarks": "Konstantin Knyrik is a pro-Russian activist running MediaGroup News Front Ltd, a news website registered in the illegally annexed Crimean Peninsula. He is the chief of the Crimean division of the Rodina Party, a pro-Kremlin party in Russia. He publicly supports Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine and is actively involved in spreading disinformation about the war.",
